Title: Visual Design
Description: Visual Design is a collaborative diagramming editor written in silverlight to support design of software systems through diagramming, mainly UML, but even other types of diagram not supported in commercial and open source tools.

Project Description
Visual Design is a collaborative diagramming editor written in silverlight to support design of software systems through diagramming, mainly UML, but even other types of diagram not supported in commercial and open source tools.


* The project is in the early stage of development *
